[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿Marc Chagall's contemporaries banished God from their works.",
        "startTime": 2273,
        "endTime": 5483,
        "slowStartTime": 3560,
        "slowEndTime": 8449
    },
    {
        "text": "But for him, painting was inconceivable without transcendence.",
        "startTime": 5759,
        "endTime": 9145,
        "slowStartTime": 8789,
        "slowEndTime": 13942
    },
    {
        "text": "As he once said, \"The artist is a messenger of God.\"",
        "startTime": 9610,
        "endTime": 12623,
        "slowStartTime": 14565,
        "slowEndTime": 19159
    },
    {
        "text": "His life is a reflection of much of the 20th century's biggest stories.",
        "startTime": 15476,
        "endTime": 19186,
        "slowStartTime": 23364,
        "slowEndTime": 29004
    },
    {
        "text": "A Russian Jew, he witnessed World War I and the Russian Revolution.",
        "startTime": 19416,
        "endTime": 22732,
        "slowStartTime": 29274,
        "slowEndTime": 34323
    },
    {
        "text": "He sought refuge in the United States after Nazi Germany's rise.",
        "startTime": 23193,
        "endTime": 26616,
        "slowStartTime": 34939,
        "slowEndTime": 40149
    },
    {
        "text": "Despite all the suffering, his painting never lost color.",
        "startTime": 28142,
        "endTime": 30901,
        "slowStartTime": 42363,
        "slowEndTime": 46577
    },
    {
        "text": "He said that it was because color is how he expressed his emotions.",
        "startTime": 31337,
        "endTime": 34693,
        "slowStartTime": 47155,
        "slowEndTime": 52265
    },
    {
        "text": "A fascination with this artistic giant...",
        "startTime": 35467,
        "endTime": 37365,
        "slowStartTime": 53350,
        "slowEndTime": 56273
    },
    {
        "text": "...has brought visitors from around the world to his exhibit.",
        "startTime": 37471,
        "endTime": 39974,
        "slowStartTime": 56356,
        "slowEndTime": 60186
    },
    {
        "text": "The message is extremely love.",
        "startTime": 42041,
        "endTime": 44759,
        "slowStartTime": 63212,
        "slowEndTime": 67364
    },
    {
        "text": "Love is the most important thing of life.",
        "startTime": 44948,
        "endTime": 48855,
        "slowStartTime": 67572,
        "slowEndTime": 73507
    },
    {
        "text": "And don't use too much your heads but your hearts.",
        "startTime": 49989,
        "endTime": 53614,
        "slowStartTime": 75134,
        "slowEndTime": 80646
    },
    {
        "text": "That's Chagall.",
        "startTime": 53833,
        "endTime": 54638,
        "slowStartTime": 80900,
        "slowEndTime": 82182
    },
    {
        "text": "The Love and Life exhibition will be in Rome until July 26th, 2016.",
        "startTime": 55423,
        "endTime": 59856,
        "slowStartTime": 83284,
        "slowEndTime": 90009
    },
    {
        "text": "It traces the life of the painter through what Chagall called the engine of life: love.",
        "startTime": 60143,
        "endTime": 64383,
        "slowStartTime": 90364,
        "slowEndTime": 96800
    },
    {
        "text": "If anything characterizes him, it is his famous scenes of lovers,...",
        "startTime": 65092,
        "endTime": 69015,
        "slowStartTime": 97788,
        "slowEndTime": 103747
    },
    {
        "text": "...all inspired by his wife Bella.",
        "startTime": 69165,
        "endTime": 70909,
        "slowStartTime": 103897,
        "slowEndTime": 106589
    },
    {
        "text": "The artist said in his autobiography that his country was his soul.",
        "startTime": 71175,
        "endTime": 74127,
        "slowStartTime": 106913,
        "slowEndTime": 111415
    },
    {
        "text": "He could travel without a passport whenever he wanted.",
        "startTime": 74468,
        "endTime": 76843,
        "slowStartTime": 111852,
        "slowEndTime": 115490
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, for a few weeks in Rome,...",
        "startTime": 77217,
        "endTime": 78968,
        "slowStartTime": 115976,
        "slowEndTime": 118677
    },
    {
        "text": "...one can join this unique artist for a short journey without carrying documents.",
        "startTime": 79319,
        "endTime": 83522,
        "slowStartTime": 119128,
        "slowEndTime": 125508
    }
]